536
00:25:59,057 --> 00:26:03,144
And Colin, despite his dinner parties
and his fucking reaching out,

537
00:26:03,228 --> 00:26:04,729
is a very bad person.

538
00:26:04,813 --> 00:26:08,233
Or maybe he's a good person
who did a very bad thing.

539
00:26:08,316 --> 00:26:09,484
To me!

540
00:26:10,151 --> 00:26:13,238
He did a very bad thing to me,
your friend.

541
00:26:13,321 --> 00:26:15,115
You don't get to have pasta with him

542
00:26:15,198 --> 00:26:18,952
