in a text!

543
00:26:20,704 --> 00:26:22,247
It actually wasn't pasta.

544
00:26:22,747 --> 00:26:25,125
I can't believe I'm even
having this conversation with you.

545
00:26:25,208 --> 00:26:27,460
It's not a conversation.
You're not letting me--

546
00:26:27,544 --> 00:26:30,547
You can't be friends with both of us,
Stanley. You have to pick.

547
00:26:31,131 --> 00:26:34,926
Uh-- Of course I'm your friend first, but…

548
00:26:37,178 --> 00:26:38,680
I shouldn't have to pick.

549
00:26:40,432 --> 00:26:41,600
[scoffs]

550
00:26:43,059 --> 00:26:44,227
You just did.

